distributions: AWS CentOS_7 RHEL_7
description: AWS CloudFormation::Init is great for integrating basic configuration management (files, services and packages) into your CloudFormation based instances or launch configurations. CodeDeploy is interesting in deploying your code to multiple AWS instances. There are lots of documentation of getting AWS::CloudFormation::Init or CodeDeploy working with Amazon Linux, but nothing on CentOS 7; so here are some snippets to get you started.

